And would I support it?

00:46:29.150 --> 00:46:31.990
And I said, well, okay,
what is the New Party

00:46:31.990 --> 00:46:32.823
all about?

00:46:32.823 --> 00:46:37.258
And they said, we want
it to be an equivalent

00:46:37.258 --> 00:46:39.950
counterbalance on the left to what

00:46:39.950 --> 00:46:43.481
the moral majority is on the right.

00:46:43.481 --> 00:46:46.433
This is the era of the moral majority.

00:46:49.060 --> 00:46:51.240
Which, moral majority
is sort of predecessor,

00:46:51.240 --> 00:46:53.557
if you like, to the tea party.

00:46:53.557 --> 00:46:56.860
And I said, well, good luck, goodbye,

00:46:56.860 --> 00:46:59.120
I hope you do well with it.

00:46:59.120 --> 00:47:00.650
And of course, there's a reason

00:47:00.650 --> 00:47:03.805
why nobody here has
heard of the New Party.

00:47:03.805 --> 00:47:07.370
because being a
counterbalance to the moral

00:47:07.370 --> 00:47:11.650
majority is not a
compelling moral narrative.

00:47:11.650 --> 00:47:15.270
The people in the moral
majority believe in something.

00:47:15.270 --> 00:47:17.090
That's why they're there.

