They're willing to internalize costs.

00:47:20.130 --> 00:47:21.410
They're willing to stay up.

00:47:21.410 --> 00:47:23.082
They're willing to go to meetings.

00:47:23.082 --> 00:47:24.540
They're willing to do something because

00:47:24.540 --> 00:47:26.350
they believe in the cause.

